53630::$$$message_0465_0000_0000$$$::A breeze enters the damp room.[lr]::
53631::$$$message_0465_0000_0001$$$::Two sets of footsteps come from the opened door.[lr]::
53632::$$$message_0465_0000_0002$$$::One is a hurried stomping, while the other sounds like it's being pulled along.::
53633::$$$message_0465_0001_0000$$$::"Come on. It's ready."[lr]::
53634::$$$message_0465_0001_0001$$$::There's a thud.[lr]::
53635::$$$message_0465_0001_0002$$$::The noise echoes through the dark, hidden room.[lr]::
53636::$$$message_0465_0001_0003$$$::Shinji Matou pushes the other person he roughly dragged into the room.::
53637::$$$message_0465_0002_0000$$$::Something is slithering and squirming on the floor.[lr]::
53638::$$$message_0465_0002_0001$$$::Shinji Matou knows what they are.[lr]::
53639::$$$message_0465_0002_0002$$$::They're the mysterious, vile creatures that his grandfather Zouken Matou has been breeding.::
53640::$$$message_0465_0003_0000$$$::   Shinji pushes someone into the room full of them.::
53641::$$$message_0465_0004_0000$$$::"There we go. Let's finish this quickly."[lr]::
53642::$$$message_0465_0004_0001$$$::He speaks from atop the stairs.[lr]::
53643::$$$message_0465_0004_0002$$$::The chamber is full of the creatures' musk. The moment any normal person steps foot into this room, they would be overcome by terror.::
53644::$$$message_0465_0005_0000$$$::But this person is an exception.[lr]::
53645::$$$message_0465_0005_0001$$$::The things shy away from the figure who just entered.[lr]::
53646::$$$message_0465_0005_0002$$$::Are they afraid, or just sick of its presence?[lr]::
53647::$$$message_0465_0005_0003$$$::The unseen monsters refuse to approach.[lr]::
53648::$$$message_0465_0005_0004$$$::They writhe and tremble in a perimeter around the figure.::
53649::$$$message_0465_0006_0000$$$::"Make me a new book. You still have two left, don't you?"[lr]::
53650::$$$message_0465_0006_0001$$$::The presence reacts to Shinji's voice.[lr]::
53651::$$$message_0465_0006_0002$$$::It creaks and scratches.[lr]::
53652::$$$message_0465_0006_0003$$$::The darkness billows and rolls, as if eager to carry out the order.::
53653::$$$message_0465_0007_0000$$$::"Do what I say, then you can go back. That's what you want, don't you?"[lr]::
53654::$$$message_0465_0007_0001$$$::There's no answer.[lr]::
53655::$$$message_0465_0007_0002$$$::Only the ear-grating chittering of the bugs fills the room.::
53656::$$$message_0465_0008_0000$$$::"Listen. We'll have to fight him sooner or later. If you keep being selfish..."[lr]::
53657::$$$message_0465_0008_0001$$$::"Then you're the one who will have to fight him," Shinji finishes.[lr]::
53658::$$$message_0465_0008_0002$$$::The figure trembles.[lr]::
53659::$$$message_0465_0008_0003$$$::It can't do that.[lr]::
53660::$$$message_0465_0008_0004$$$::The old man whom Shinji calls his teacher won't allow it.::
53661::$$$message_0465_0009_0000$$$::But the figure knows that Shinji doesn't always follow his teacher's directions.[lr]::
53662::$$$message_0465_0009_0001$$$::Right now, he's filled with hatred for Shirou Emiya.[lr]::
53663::$$$message_0465_0009_0002$$$::His mind has long since lost any patience for rejection.[lr]::
53664::$$$message_0465_0009_0003$$$::The old man is keeping him away from the conflict for his own safety, but to Shinji, it's an unacceptable humiliation.::
53665::$$$message_0465_0010_0000$$$::"......"[lr]::
53666::$$$message_0465_0010_0001$$$::After a long silence, a change occurs in the room.[lr]::
53667::$$$message_0465_0010_0002$$$::Another figure appears in a flash of light.[lr]::
53668::$$$message_0465_0010_0003$$$::The creatures' presence is driven from the room by her appearance.[lr]::
53669::$$$message_0465_0010_0004$$$::Even these vermin of low intelligence know to fear her enormous, monstrous aura.::
53670::$$$message_0465_0011_0000$$$::"Good. You can leave everything else to me."[lr]::
53671::$$$message_0465_0011_0001$$$::Her body is slender and supple. Her hair, long enough to reach the floor. [lr]::
53672::$$$message_0465_0011_0002$$$::Clad in a single black garment, she is the Servant Rider.::
53673::$$$message_0465_0012_0000$$$::"Let me ask you a question, Shinji.[lr]::
53674::$$$message_0465_0012_0001$$$::Will you only use me to protect yourself?"[lr]::
53675::$$$message_0465_0012_0002$$$::In the depths of the chamber,[lr]::
53676::$$$message_0465_0012_0003$$$::gazing up from the bottom of the pen, the dark Servant inquires.::
53677::$$$message_0465_0013_0000$$$::"Yeah. I need you to keep me safe if anything crazy happens."[lr]::
53678::$$$message_0465_0013_0001$$$::Shinji, a Master once again, fails to contain his delight. He's so ecstatic that he blurts out an answer which can only be a lie.::

